IS  - 4
PB  - Academy of Management
N2  - The article looks at a questionnaire of personnel directors regarding state of sensitivity training as utilized within large scale business firms. Techniques used to improve organizational effectiveness are discussed including sensitivity training through ?T-groups.? The author questions the use of such techniques by firms in the training of their managerial team. Responses to the questionnaire are examined to assess the perceived effectiveness of management development according to standard industrial classifications.
AB  - The article looks at a questionnaire of personnel directors regarding state of sensitivity training as utilized within large scale business firms. Techniques used to improve organizational effectiveness are discussed including sensitivity training through ?T-groups.? The author questions the use of such techniques by firms in the training of their managerial team. Responses to the questionnaire are examined to assess the perceived effectiveness of management development according to standard industrial classifications.
